text: Callimedusa is a genus of frogs in the family Phyllomedusidae. The frogs in this genus live in South America. Species: *Callimedusa atelopoides *Callimedusa baltea *Callimedusa duellmani *Callimedusa ecuatoriana *Callimedusa perinesos *Callimedusa tomopterna ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Callimedusa
